title: Extra Fine Crepe Paper by Lia Griffith, high quality crepe paper for flower making
description:
Extra fine crepe paper by Lia Griffith in a set of gorgeous colours. This is a high-quality crepe paper designed for creating paper flowers. 

This is the type of paper I use myself to create the most delicate blooms and I have to say that is a wonderful paper to work with! This collection of colours work together beautifully and the two shades of green are my all-time favourite. 

The rolls are 25cm x 100cm and this extra fine crepe paper is lightweight with 130% stretch.

Colours available are Vanilla, Chiffon, Blush, Coral, Honeysuckle, Cranberry, Sangria, Aubergine, Green Tea and Cypress.

I offer individual rolls for you to create your own palette or you could use the set of 7 colours that will include: Chiffon, Coral, Honeysuckle, Cranberry, Sangria, Aubergine and Cypress. 

Thanks!
Rebeca

title: Crepe paper Peony printable tutorial, Home decoration project supply, DIY paper flower lesson
description:
Crepe paper Peony printable tutorial, Home decoration project supply, DIY paper flower lesson

Peonies are gorgeous flowers! They are amazing for home decoration, for wedding bouquets, for gifts... And the most special thing in the paper Peonies is the time you invest to create them. So, as a gift one paper Peony, made by you, is priceless...
Do you want to learn how to make them? This tutorial is easy and suitable even for beginners. 

This listing contains: 1 PDF file with 20 pages Crepe paper Peony flower tutorial

Skills level: Confident beginner, Beginner

With this tutorial you will learn how to be a real paper flower creator. The tutorial doesn’t include ready to cut files or templates for plotters and cutting machines. Every petal and leaf you will have to shape by yourself. This process will train your brain in how to make decisions about the sizes, shapes and materials you use and will train your fingers in how to shape and sculpt the paper pieces. Actually, you will learn how to model, from scratch, very realistic paper flowers, which will be absolutely your own creations and will amaze everyone who sees them. 
If you involve in this craft process your little ones, the work with these different materials will improve their fine motor skills and their brains.

You will receive a printable PDF file with 22 pages and 47 detailed photos with step by step instructions on how to make a Peony from crepe paper. The Peony on the cover pictures was made using the same process. 


*****

title: Cyclamen Keepsake A5 Christmas Card
description:
This A5 Illustrated Card with keepsake Cyclamen flowers and foliage is a beautiful handmade gift and card in one! 

The card is printed on quality 320gsm ‘Cairn Straw’ recycled white Kraft card which has a natural fleck throughout and is lined with a 135gsm white insert, this is blank. There is an option to personalise the card with your own message, so it can be sent direct to the lucky recipient if required.

Each flower is made from Italian crepe and can be easily detached from the card and inserted into the mini clay flower holder also included, to create a gorgeous decoration for many years to come.

A small gift tag also attached to the card can be personalised with a short message, printed with 'Merry Christmas' or left blank so you can write your own. The tag can be removed along with the flowers or left to hang on the card, by simply re-tying the hemp twine once the flowers have been removed.

The card will be supplied in a Kraft gift box with a removable label on the front, which reads 'To' and 'From' with space for you to write names, etc, or again this can be personalised if required.

Add a deep picture frame to your order for that extra special gift, the frame is available to purchase in black and has a Perspex front. It can be used wall mounted as well as freestanding. The frame measures 20 x 25 cm and is 6cm in depth. Please note the frame will be supplied ready to mount the card which will be packaged in a Kraft gift box as shown. 

An outer cardboard wrap will be used to give extra protection to the card and box when posting.

title: Santa Claus- Retro Handmade Christmas Ornament
description:
Santa Claus - Retro Handmade Christmas Ornament 

I hand painted his face on a watte spun cotton ball and added a chenille beard and crepe paper hat. His body & suit are formed out of chenille pipe cleaners, accented with a crepe paper belt & boots and seed bead buttons. He's holding a little pipe cleaner candy cane.  

His hanger is a loop of crinkle wire. He can hang from a tree or stocking by the loop, or you could add a hook. He'd also be a cute accent to a gift package or a snow scene.


 4.25" tall x 2.5", the head is .75" across



I styled this after 50's & 60's style ornaments. I've always loved the old ornaments with the little pipe cleaner bodies and expressive faces. When I saw they still make the bump Chenille Pipe Cleaners I was inspired to make some of my own – and have been having a really great time doing so.



Shipping is estimated, and I'll combine shipping to reduce cost. I'll refund any overage over a dollar. I package to ensure items arrive in good condition, but try to reuse & recycle whenever possible for the environment so I use recycled and new packing materials depending on what I have on hand.

Don't hesitate to let me know if you'd like to see any additional photos.
